commentPostTextItems.html: Voges is the Man of the Match: " I think new players bring fresh energy. It was also great for Marsh and Haddin (he's not new) to get an opportunity."
Watson: "We held our nerve. Voges was absolutely amazing. They were cruising along at one stage and I knew they will take risks at some stage. I'm very excited to get on that plane to India."

West Indies won't be on that plane back home yet. There's the T20 at the Gabba on Wednesday. Their last chance to salvage a win in what's been a miserable tour. Do join us for that. Thanks for your company today. Cheers!
